TITLE: AlertDialog with Image Implementation in React
DESCRIPTION: Implements an AlertDialog component with an image, promotional text, and an upgrade button. Shows a discount offer with a promo code in a styled dialog box with responsive layout.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gluestack/gluestack-ui/blob/main/example/storybook-nativewind/src/components/AlertDialog/index.nw.stories.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { AlertDialog, AlertDialogContent, AlertDialogBody, AlertDialogBackdrop } from "@/components/ui/alert-dialog";
import { Box } from "@/components/ui/box";
import { Button, ButtonText } from "@/components/ui/button";
