TITLE: Implementing Multiple Modal Dialogs with gluestack-ui in React
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates the implementation of multiple layered modals for a password reset flow. The example shows three connected modals: a forgot password form, a verification code entry, and a new password setup screen. Each modal includes appropriate navigation buttons and form inputs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gluestack/gluestack-ui/blob/main/example/storybook/src/ui/components/Overlay/Modal/index.stories.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_6

