TITLE: Customizing Typography Tokens with createConfig in gluestack-ui
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to customize typography tokens in gluestack-ui by using the createConfig function. It shows how to import the default configuration and override specific token values, such as adding a new font size while preserving other default tokens.
