TITLE: Configuration with Custom Theme Path
DESCRIPTION: Babel configuration with custom theme path and styled alias options
SOURCE: https://github.com/gluestack/gluestack-ui/blob/main/example/storybook/src/styled/advanced/BabelPlugins/index.stories.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const path = require('path');
const gluestackStyleResolver = require('@gluestack-style/babel-plugin-styled-resolver');

module.exports = function (api) {
  api.cache(true);
  return {
    presets: ['babel-preset-expo'],
    plugins: [
      [
        gluestackStyleResolver,
        {
          configThemePath: ['config', 'theme'],
        },
      ],
    ],
  };
};
```

