TITLE: Mapping React Component Props to CSS Classes in Gluestack UI
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how various styling props used in Gluestack UI components map to corresponding CSS class names. It demonstrates the translation pattern from React component props to Tailwind-like utility classes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gluestack/gluestack-ui/blob/main/example/storybook-nativewind/src/guides/more/Upgrade to v2/index.nw.stories.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
// Margin right property
{`mr="value"`}  className="mr-value"

// Flex property
{`flex={value}`}  className="flex-value"

// Flex direction property
{`flexDirection="value"`}  className="flex-value"

// Line height property
{`lineHeight="value"`}  className="leading-value"

// Height property
{`h="value"`}  className="h-[value]"

// Align self property
{`alignSelf="value"`}  className="self-value"

// Position property
{`position="value"`}  className="position-value"

// Max width property
{`maxWidth="value"`}  className="max-w-value"

// Max height property
{`maxHeight="value"`}  className="max-h-value"

// Min width property
{`minWidth="value"`}  className="min-w-value"

// Min height property
{`minHeight="value"`}  className="min-h-value"

// Font family property
{`fontFamily="value"`}  className="font-value"

// Font style property
{`fontStyle="value"`}  className="value"

// Font size property
{`fontSize="value"`}  className="text-value"

// Top position property
{`top={value}`}  className="top-value"

// Bottom position property
{`bottom={value}`}  className="bottom-value"

// Left position property
{`left={value}`}  className="left-value"

// Right position property
{`right={value}`}  className="right-value"

// Z-index property
{`zIndex={value}`}  className="z-value"

// Shadow color property
{`shadowColor="value"`}  className="shadow-value"

// Overflow property
{`overflow="value"`}  className="overflow-value"

// Text align property
{`textAlign="value"`}  className="text-value"

// Display property
{`display="value"`}  className="hidden / flex / block / inline"

// Responsive design - small breakpoint
{`$sm={value}`}  className="sm:value"

// Responsive design - medium breakpoint
{`$md={value}`}  className="md:value"

// Responsive design - large breakpoint
{`$lg={value}`}  className="lg:value"
```

